Data License Notice
===================

The CODE in this repository is licensed under the MIT License above.

The PROCESSED DATA in 01_data/processed/ and 01_data/external/ is derived
from multiple public sources, each retaining its original license:

  - USDA ERS International Agricultural Productivity: U.S. Public Domain
  - IDB Agrimonitor: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0)
  - World Bank WDI / APER / Tapping Potential: Creative Commons CC BY 4.0
  - FAOSTAT (via Our World in Data): Creative Commons CC BY 4.0
  - MEFP Bolivia fiscal bulletins: Public data under DS 28168/2005
  - INE Bolivia statistics: Public data
  - geoBoundaries: Creative Commons CC BY 4.0

Derived datasets in this repository inherit these licenses. Users should
cite original sources per the CITATION.cff file and the Anexo A of the
project report.

Attribution is required when redistributing derived data.
